title: Gravity Falls Complete S01 (1080p, WEB-DL, M4V)
description:
Gravity Falls, Complete Season 1.

Since the season just ended, I decided to collect all the WEB-DLs of the series, transcode them as 1080p M4Vs with tags (For use with iTunes, etc.) and give them back.

If you wanna play them with something that doesn't understand M4Vs, change the extension for MP4 (This files are Standard MPEG-4 AVC, just with iTunes naming conventions)

Have fun, and enjoy the series!

Note: I have only 15Mb U/L speed, but I'll try to keep seeding as long as I can. After grabbing it, keep seeding it, so it can stay alive!
